<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.4">
<l>tāṅkā tatōrā ḷariyā yavuṇaṉ ṟaṉaivī ṭamuṉin tavaṉā lamarum</l>
<l>pūṅkō taiyarpoṅ kerimūḻ kaviḷait tatuvaṉ  ṟiyumveṉ ṟikoḷvā ḷamaril</l>
<l>pāṅkā kamuṉai varoṭaṉ paḷavip patiṟṟain tiraṭṭip paṭaivēn tarpaṭa</l>
<l>nīṅkāc ceruvil niṟaikāt tavaṉuk kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for the one who, besides becoming an unstoppable man-lion</l>
<l rend="indent">raging at the demon so [he] perished,</l>
<l>The cause of the flower-decked [ladies] who dwelled with that [demon]</l>
<l rend="indent">to plunge in the shooting flames,</l>
<l>Protected [Draupadī’s] virtue when he killed the one-hundred armed kings,</l>
<l rend="indent">having loyally joined in affection with the Five</l>
<l>Long ago on the deadly field of victory, is the great mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
